title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a highlight or map, an exception is thrown.
EB: Exporting data from a table containing a highlight or map should not result in an exception.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Attempt to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map.
